name: PUSSY PASSWORD \ 猫的密码
description:
This game is a very interesting project in terms of the fact that you have the opportunity to
enjoy a beautiful cartoon design, pleasant music, to rub out on beautiful girls, and most importantly
to train your brain with the solution of different mathematical expressions

You can play, enjoy a nice design and look at beautiful girls.
You will have to solve mathematical expressions for a certain time and for each game you have only 3 lives.

Game features:
  • Cartoon Design
  • Beautiful girls
  • Interesting mathematical expressions
  • The ability to train the brain
